Title: The Healing of Shen-zin Su
Description:
This is what comes of such recklessness. How could he think this was even a possibility?

Nevermind, there's no time for that now. We need to act to save Shen-zin Su.

Find any healers you can! Rescue them, relieve them - whatever you need to do to get them over here healing the wound.

Keep the healers safe at all costs!
ObjectivesText: Rescue and defend healers until Shen-zin Su's wound is healed.
